{"product_id":"shanaya-attar-roll-on-6ml-al-saalim-perfumers-alcohol-free","title":"Shanaya Attar (Roll On 6ml) | Al-Saalim Perfumers | Alcohol Free","description":"\u003cp\u003e  Experience elegance and charm with Shanaya Attar by Al-Saalim Perfumers.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eShanaya is a beautifully crafted fragrance with a soft, sweet, and slightly floral aroma, designed to feel graceful and luxurious.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis attar is perfect for those who enjoy smooth, feminine, and classy scents. It is suitable for daily wear, special occasions, festive events, and evening use. The alcohol-free formula ensures it is gentle on the skin while offering a long-lasting and pleasant fragrance.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eKey Features\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFragrance Type: Soft, Sweet \u0026amp; Floral\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eQuantity: 6 ml Roll On\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAlcohol Free\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLong Lasting \u0026amp; Elegant Aroma\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePremium glass roll-on bottle\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSuitable for women \u0026amp; those who prefer soft fragrances\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhy Choose Shanaya Attar\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGraceful and luxurious fragrance\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePerfect for daily wear and special moments\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSkin-friendly and non-irritating\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePremium packaging, ideal for gifting\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHow to Use\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eApply lightly on pulse points such as the neck, wrists, or behind the ears for a lasting and elegant fragrance.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"AL-SAALIM PERFUMES","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50472868184311,"sku":null,"price":179.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0923\/0755\/4551\/files\/DBA449C5-395D-41C6-91CE-FD450F9FA907.png?v=1777870289","url":"https:\/\/alsaalimperfume.shop\/products\/shanaya-